text: Excellent Location!  Cottage as described.  Quaint and rustic but has everything you need.   It really is a very quiet and secluded location in the heart of Austin.  Less than 1/4 mile from lake path, Deep Eddy and restaurants.  I commuted to downtown by bike or took the bus (4 line very easy!).  Jonathan was extremely accommodating, communicative and checked in on me frequently.   Appreciate the stay!  Keep Austin Weird!!
title: Quaint Cottage - West of Downtown
